Gerbera UPnP Media Server - https://gerbera.io
Usage:
  gerbera [OPTION...]

  -D, --debug           Enable debugging
      --debug-mode arg  Set Debugging Mode
  -d, --daemon          Daemonize after startup
  -u, --user arg        Drop privs to user
  -P, --pidfile arg     Write a pidfile to the specified location, e.g.
                        /run/gerbera.pid
  -e, --interface arg   Interface to bind with
  -p, --port arg        Port to bind with, must be >=49152
  -i, --ip arg          IP to bind with
  -c, --config arg      Path to config file
  -m, --home arg        Search this directory for a .config/gerbera folder
                        containing a config file
  -f, --cfgdir arg      Override name of config folder (.config/gerbera) in
                        home folder.
  -l, --logfile arg     Set log location
      --compile-info    Print compile info and exit
  -v, --version         Print version info and exit
  -h, --help            Print this help and exit
      --create-config   Print a default config.xml file and exit
      --check-config    Check config.xml file and exit
      --offline         Do not answer UPnP content requests
      --add-file FILE   Scan a file into the DB on startup, can be specified
                        multiple times
